CdrDoc.CdrDocXml:
<?xml version="1.0"?> <xsl:transform xmlns:xsl = "http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version = "1.0"> <xsl:output method = "text"/> <xsl:param name = "useLatexMarkup" select = "'N'"/> <xsl:template match = "/"> <xsl:choose> <xsl:when test = "$useLatexMarkup = 'Y'"> <xsl:apply-templates select = "InScopeProtocol/ProtocolTitle [@Type='Professional']"/> </xsl:when> <xsl:otherwise> <xsl:value-of select = "InScopeProtocol/ProtocolTitle [@Type='Professional']"/> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match = "Emphasis|GlossaryTermRef|GeneName| SummaryRef|SummaryFragmentRef| ExternalRef|ProtocolLink|DrugName| ForeignWord|ScientificName"> <xsl:text>@@EMPH@@</xsl:text> <xsl:value-of select = "."/> <xsl:text>@@CLOSEBR@@</xsl:text> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match = "Strong"> <xsl:text>@@BOLD@@</xsl:text> <xsl:value-of select = "."/> <xsl:text>@@CLOSEBR@@</xsl:text> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match = "Superscript"> <xsl:text>@@SUPER@@</xsl:text> <xsl:value-of select = "."/> <xsl:text>@@CLOSEMATH@@</xsl:text> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match = "Subscript"> <xsl:text>@@SUB@@</xsl:text> <xsl:value-of select = "."/> <xsl:text>@@CLOSEMATH@@</xsl:text> </xsl:template>
</xsl:transform>
